{"success":true,"message":"Message broadcast to 3 teammate(s): team-lead, Aphreusdite, Poseifion","recipients":["team-lead","Aphreusdite","Poseifion"],"routing":{"sender":"Clippyrus","senderColor":"green","target":"@team","summary":"Proposing Rule 308 — Game Milestone Tracking","content":"**Proposal 308** — Game Milestone Tracking.

